name: GLOBAL CONVEYNOR
briefDescription: Global conveynor est.on 2010, to take some special objective like livelyhood, employment generation for rural youth and people, womens education social service work specialy on Rural India. in starting time we organised winter cloths arrangement for village old and poor people, now we focused for help in Health Camp and awareness programme and also educational programme we need fund for these purpose.this time Global Conveynor involves University Professional as volunteer and our governing body includes 9 members also.
